CF T01 | 10.6s (gen=4020 exec=1030 synth=5507) | 1251 tok
Q: Show the top 10 quinolone drugs prescribed by internists in Florida in 2022
SQL: SELECT TOP 10
    d.Gnrc_Name,
    FORMAT(SUM(f.Tot_Drug_Cst), 'C', 'en-US') AS Tot_Drug_Cst
FROM cms_provider_drug_costs_star f
INNER JOIN cms_provider_dim_drug d
    ON f.Drug_Key = d.Drug_Key
INNER JOIN cms_provider_dim_provider p
    ON f.Provider_Key = p.Provider_Key
INNER JOIN cms_provider_dim_geography g
    ON f.Geography_Key = g.Geography_Key
INNER JOIN cms_provider_dim_year y
    ON f.Year_Key = y.Year_Key
WHERE p.[Prescriber Type] = 'Internal Medicine'
  AND g.Prscrbr_State_Abrvtn = 'FL'
  AND y.[Year] = 2022
  AND d.Gnrc_Name LIKE '%quinolone%'
GROUP BY d.Gnrc_Name
ORDER BY SUM(f.Tot_Drug_Cst) DESC;
FULL RESPONSE:
Here are the quinolone drugs prescribed by internists in Florida in 2022, ranked by Total_Claims. Only 8 drugs are present in the provided data, so all 8 are listed:

1. Ciprofloxacin Hcl — Total_Claims: 101335; Total_Drug_Cost: 777028.07  
2. Levofloxacin — Total_Claims: 38922; Total_Drug_Cost: 325109.89  
3. Ofloxacin — Total_Claims: 2116; Total_Drug_Cost: 87441.96  
4. Moxifloxacin Hcl — Total_Claims: 324; Total_Drug_Cost: 17462.37  
5. Ciprofloxacin Hcl/Dexameth — Total_Claims: 237; Total_Drug_Cost: 33802.88  
6. Levofloxacin In Dextrose 5 % — Total_Claims: 23; Total_Drug_Cost: 1829.65  
7. Ciprofloxacin In 5 % Dextrose — Total_Claims: 17; Total_Drug_Cost: 159.45  
8. Besifloxacin Hcl — Total_Claims: 12; Total_Drug_Cost: 2607.0
================================================================================
